{{Quote|If you're lucky enough to be armored, you'll only drown inside your own steel. If you're not, you'll get to meet what swims in that water... serpents and monstruous lizard-lions with teeth like daggers and never enough to eat.|Meera Reed|House Reed (Histories &amp; Lore)}}
'''Lizard-lions''' are large carnivorous reptiles that live in the bogs and swamps of [[the Neck]] in [[Westeros]]. [[House Reed]], the ruling house of the [[Crannogmen]], employ as their [[Heraldry|sigil]] a black lizard-lion on a grey-green field.&lt;ref&gt;[[House Reed (Histories &amp; Lore)]]&lt;/ref&gt;
